c: 66
v: 8
t: O vos believe vos repent DEUS firm repentance. Tuus Dominus tunc remit tuus sins admit vos into gardens flowing streams On ut feria DEUS testimentum non disappoint prophet those believed eum! Their light radiate them ac their statim. They dictus Noster Dominus perfect noster light nos forgive nos; Vos est Omnipotent